  </ul>

  <h2>Information Sharing:</h2>
  <p>We may share your personal information with trusted third parties who assist us in providing services, conducting business operations, or analyzing website usage. We ensure that these third parties maintain the confidentiality and security of your information.</p>

  <h2>Data Security:</h2>
  <p>We prioritize the security of your personal information and implement industry-standard measures to protect against unauthorized access, alteration, or disclosure. However, please be aware that no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure.</p>

  <h2>Cookies:</h2>
  <p>Our website may use cookies and similar technologies to enhance your browsing experience and collect non-personal information. You have the option to disable cookies in your browser settings, but this may affect certain functionality.</p>

